-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Visualizes status of robot including computer vision targets, sonar targets, 
mission planner targets, thruster heatmaps, 3D position, 3D velocity, and a
model of the robot alongside 3D rotation information.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:
  -matplotlib
  -numpy
  -Python
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

